headline: Stock Market Today: Dow, S&P Waffle As Netflix, GE Aerospace Earnings Loom (Live Coverage)
summary: The Dow Jones Industrial Average and other major stock indexes wavered in afternoon trading Friday as Wall Street looked ahead to a three-day weekend. Among the winners was obesity drug stock Novo Nordisk, which surged on the stock market today.

headline: 1 Services Stock to Target This Week and 2 That Underwhelm
summary: Business services providers use their specialized expertise to help enterprises streamline operations and cut costs. These firms have helped their customers unlock huge efficiencies, so it’s no surprise the industry has posted a 11.8% gain over the past six months, nearly mirrorring the S&P 500.
